//i.ytimg.com/vi/nrZyGzOgtL8/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FnrZyGzOgtL8%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=0f5ae62b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《義勇軍進行曲》，中國的國歌，所有中國人都耳熟能詳。 但國歌作詞人田漢的悲慘下場：文革期間被批鬥致死，又未必是每個人都知道這段歷史。"},{"pid":"f3fdcb3ea8a6ef13a81c8f4db29e50a7ae22386d","tid":2064242,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:24:56.000Z","msg":"逼人愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦我愛香港國"},{"pid":"5475cf476783df6d6f59edd137dd6e92ee720b51","tid":2064242,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091d2cc18c5b8109901371597e19e7e05a57df3a","tid":2064242,"uid":315376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T18:17:14.000Z","msg":"當幾個簡單既拍子 幾句唱得出香港人心聲既歌詞 都比佢套上惡毒既字眼 來形容<br />\n我想像唔到佢究竟有幾有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}